此文件夹下的config.json 都为例程，需要把你的节点信息outbound替换进去

#chnroute mode:
sh /etc/storage/v2ray/start-whitelist.sh

#stop v2ray:
sh /etc/storage/v2ray/stop.sh

#gfwlist mode:

FIRST:
edit & copy config-gfw.json to /etc/storage/v2ray/

THEN:
sh /etc/storage/v2ray/start-gfwlist.sh


